span.span: READING TIME WITH LILLIE & THE LIZARDS

It isn't only the teachers who are missing the kids being at school. Our school pets miss seeing all their friends, too! The staff has been making up for it by spending some quality reading time with them!

span.span: Students! We miss you! We can't wait to have you back at school! We wanted to share our feelings in this video we made.

div.p: Purpose - The purpose of Bertha-Hewitts learning plan is to provide our PreK 12th grade students with meaningful lessons as a continuance of the education they were receiving prior to Governor Walzs Directive to shutdown schools due to the Coronavirus outbreak. This is not an ideal situation but as you plan your lessons think about the essential standards and activities children need to know to finish the grade or class they are currently in. Every class that our students partake in is a vital part of their overall education. Thank you for putting in time to ensure they are continuing to get as quality of an education as possible in each of the classes.
